Package: autoannotatecelltype
Type: Package
Title: Automated Cell Type Annotation Using AI Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Hutchinson", , "john@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package provides automated cell type annotation functionality 
    using large language models (Claude and Gemini) to identify cell types from 
    marker gene lists. The package is designed for single-cell RNA sequencing 
    analysis workflows and supports multiple species and tissue contexts.
